metadata.name: Alien
metadata.description:
Dazed, like a ‘stranger’
Among people who are not like her!… 
Astonishingly watching her surroundings as if she was looking for someone familiar!…

[Alien]
My intuitive sketching (drawing) of a portrait and the first NFT of my portrait collection is on the Foundation.

With expressive pencil lines on paper,
The closer you look, the more details you will see!
